io.confluent.ksql.rest

Class SessionProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.rest.SessionProperties

  • public class SessionProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps the incoming KsqlRequest streamsProperties in a object withthe KsqlHostInfo and URL of the server that handles the request. This should be created in the Rest Resource that receives the request.
